#   No-name AliExpress / Amazon "smart"     usually "Yoosee" / "iCSee"
#     cams under $30                        ecosystem; RTSP support is
#                                           inconsistent or undocumented
#   Wyze v3 + "RTSP firmware"               works, but Wyze abandoned
#                                           it ~2022; not safe to expose
#                                           on the network long-term

